long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Set one of the 7 wonders of the world as the background in your browser new tab.

🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍

This is a free add-on for Chrome Browser where the primary target is to set a background from our selective 7 wonders images gallery powered by Unsplash in your Chrome Browser default new tab. We are actually changing your Chrome browser default new tab page.

🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍🌍

Also as an added feature, we are giving you an easy way to search your desired information, images, video, and more through Microsoft Bing search. There is also a digital clock in new tabs where you can check your current location time in 12 hour/ 24-hour format according to your preference.
